name from joseph desire mobutu to mobutu sese seko translated as 
the all powerful warrior who 
mobutu also nationalized key industries and replaced foreigners 
with zaireans at their helm production collapsed along with much 
of countrys infrastructure mobutu was accused of plundering 
zaires wealth his critics say he amassed several billion dollars 
twice he needed major western military intervention to put down 
