here are brief sketches of the five 
discovery crew members 
air force col loren j shriver is making his second trip into 
space as commander of discovery on its mission to deploy the 15 
billion hubble space telescope 
shriver heads a crew of space veterans on the flight the last 
time the national aeronautics and space administration flew a crew 
