expressed interest in establishing relations with both the united 
states and the soviet union 
the united states and albania have had no diplomatic ties since 
1939 albania is one of a handful of countries with which the 
united states does not have such ties 
since alia came to office in 1985 he has slowly attempted to 
end the isolationist policies imposed by his predecessor enver 
hoxha albania broke relations with the soviet union in 1961 
because hoxha felt that moscow was deviating from marxist ideology 
after noting alias expression of interest in restoring ties 
