dakota during the afternoon a severe thunderstorm watch was issued 
for parts of minnesota and wisconsin 
showers were widely scattered from southeastern kansas to 
northeastern texas and from the upper great lakes to the central 
high plains 
thunderstorms over minnesota during the morning produced hail an 
inch in diameter at royalton about 20 miles north of st cloud 
from late monday into early tuesday thunderstorms produced 
severe weather in the southern plains with 36 reports of severe 
weather in western texas and western oklahoma the national weather 
service said 
