he said it is from our point of view the best piece of 
legislation weve seen emerge from congress to protect the 
diversity principle 
however the bill has not yet been passed and a court appeal of 
the original federal order has sent that back to greene for 
reconsideration johnson said 
the outcome will determine whether the newspaper industry is 
going to face a whole new group of competitors in the electronic 
information services he said 
