the man who built a bomb that maimed a 
5yearold girl at a k mart store a year ago committed suicide 
within 36 hours of the blast authorities said tuesday 
david l swinford 19 shot himself in the head as he sat in a 
car on a rural road on april 19 1989 a few hours after having 
discussed the bombing with his mother and stepfather said charles 
petersen resident agent in charge of the us bureau of alcohol 
tobacco and firearms in indianapolis 
