it was a stunning and poignant moment of truth even for veteran 
visitors to manhattan federal court where towering figures ranging 
from john mitchell to leona helmsley have been digested and spit 
out as felons 
its a tragedy to see historys greatest financier so 
humbled said theodore wells a prominent defense attorney and 
